| Error Code | HTTP Status | Description | Example Scenario |
|------------|-------------|-------------|------------------|
| LIC-001 | 400 | Invalid license scope | Scope value not in [GLOBAL, NATIONAL, STATE] |
| LIC-002 | 400 | Missing required field | HON, scope, country, or licenseType is null |
| LIC-003 | 400 | State required for STATE scope | Scope=STATE but state field is empty |
| LIC-004 | 404 | License source not found | GET request for non-existent HON |
