### 9.2 Monitoring Strategy

#### 9.2.1 Key Metrics

**Application Metrics**:
- API response times (avg, p50, p95, p99)
- Request throughput (requests/second)
- Error rates by endpoint
- Active connections
- JVM memory usage
- Thread pool utilization

**Database Metrics**:
- MongoDB query performance
- Connection pool usage
- Index usage statistics
- Document count
- Storage size

**Elasticsearch Metrics**:
- Query performance
- Index size
- Shard health
- Search latency

**Business Metrics**:
- Total license sources count
- Active vs inactive records
- Excel uploads per day
- Search queries per day
- Top searched license types

#### 9.2.2 Logging Strategy

**Log Levels**:
- **ERROR**: System errors, exceptions
- **WARN**: Validation failures, business rule violations
- **INFO**: API requests, business operations
- **DEBUG**: Detailed execution flow (dev/staging only)

**Log Format**:
```
[timestamp] [level] [thread] [class] - [message] [context]
```

**Sample Logs**:
```
2024-03-24 10:00:00 INFO [http-nio-8080-exec-1] LicenseSourceService - Creating license source with HON: LIC-USA-CA-MED-001
2024-03-24 10:00:01 ERROR [http-nio-8080-exec-1] LicenseSourceService - Failed to create license source: Duplicate HON
2024-03-24 10:05:00 INFO [http-nio-8080-exec-2] LicenseMigrationController - Excel upload started: license_data.xlsx, size: 1000 records
2024-03-24 10:05:25 INFO [http-nio-8080-exec-2] LicenseMigrationProcessor - Excel processing complete: 980 success, 20 failed
```

#### 9.2.3 Alerting

**Alert Conditions**:
- API response time > 1 second (sustained for 5 minutes)
- Error rate > 5% (in last 10 minutes)
- Database connection failures
- Elasticsearch indexing failures
- Disk space < 20%
- Memory usage > 85%
- Application downtime

**Alert Channels**:
- Email notifications
- Slack/Teams messages
- PagerDuty (for critical alerts)

