## Appendix B: Error Codes

| Error Code | HTTP Status | Description | Resolution |
|------------|-------------|-------------|------------|
| LIC-001 | 400 | Invalid license scope | Use GLOBAL, NATIONAL, or STATE |
| LIC-002 | 400 | Missing required field | Provide all required fields |
| LIC-003 | 400 | State required for STATE scope | Provide state when scope is STATE |
| LIC-004 | 404 | License source not found | Verify HON exists |
| LIC-005 | 409 | Duplicate HON | Use unique HON identifier |
| LIC-006 | 413 | File size exceeds limit | Reduce file size to < 10MB |
| LIC-007 | 500 | Database error | Contact support |
| LIC-008 | 500 | Elasticsearch error | Contact support |
| LIC-009 | 400 | Invalid file format | Use .xlsx format only |
| LIC-010 | 400 | Too many records in batch | Limit to 100 records per request |

