## Appendix C: Glossary

| Term | Definition |
|------|------------|
| **HON** | Unique Number - Unique identifier for each license source |
| **Scope** | Geographic scope of license (GLOBAL, NATIONAL, STATE) |
| **License Type** | Category of professional license (e.g., Medical, Legal, Engineering) |
| **Governing Agency** | Regulatory body that issues/manages the license |
| **Smart Search** | Elasticsearch-powered full-text search with facets |
| **Filter Search** | MongoDB-based exact match search with filters |
| **Soft Delete** | Marking record as inactive instead of physical deletion |
| **Bulk Upsert** | Batch operation that inserts new or updates existing records |
| **MapStruct** | Java library for type-safe bean mapping |
| **Apache POI** | Java library for reading/writing Microsoft Office files |

